OL,3,CHealthcare assistant jailed for
OL,4,Cnegligence after death of mental
OL,5,Chealth patient
OL,7,FA healthcare assistant has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor negligence after failing to check
OL,9,Fon a patient at a mental health unit
OL,10,Fin Nottinghamshire who took her own
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FPolice say Rebecca Welch, 29, failed
OL,14,Fto carry out appropriate observations
OL,15,Fon the welfare of Amelia Rose, 31, at
OL,16,FMillbrook Mental Health Unit in Sutton-
OL,17,Fin-Ashfield.
OL,19,FWelch was supposed to check on her at
OL,20,F10-minute intervals from 1pm on 31
OL,21,FJanuary 2020.
