OL,7,FCCTV footage revealed that Welch
OL,8,Ffailed to conduct any checks at all
OL,9,Fbefore Amelia was found by another
OL,10,Fmember of staff at 1.53pm.
OL,12,FAmelia was transferred to King's Mill
OL,13,FHospital but died the next day.
OL,15,FIt was also discovered during
OL,16,Finvestigations that Welch had falsely
OL,17,Frecorded observations every 10 minutes
OL,18,Fin a log.
