OL,7,FAn inquest held in 2022 found Amelia
OL,8,Fhad most likely died by her own hand
OL,9,Fbut it was not possible to determine
OL,10,Fher intent.
OL,12,FWelch was charged with wilful neglect
OL,13,Fby a care worker.
OL,15,FWelch pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,16,Fhearing and was convicted and
OL,17,Fsentenced to one year in jail at
OL,18,FNottingham Crown Court on Wednesday 4
OL,19,FSeptember.
OL,21,FIn a statement, Amelia's parents said:
