OL,5,Chealth patient
OL,7,F"Our beautiful, fun-loving, caring and
OL,8,Fintelligent daughter Amelia Rose died
OL,9,Faged 31, in what should have been the
OL,10,Fprime of her life.
OL,12,F"Amelia would have had her whole life
OL,13,Fahead of her if she had been given the
OL,14,Fhelp she so desperately pleaded for,
OL,15,Fbut in three short days of admission
OL,16,Fto Millbrook, due to the complete lack
OL,17,Fof care by Rebecca Welch, she was left
OL,18,Fto die unnecessarily.
