OL,7,F"We will never see the wonderful
OL,8,Fperson she would have become, a loving
OL,9,Fdaughter, sister, aunty and
OL,10,Fpotentially a mother. Our lives will
OL,11,Fnever be the same again."
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Clare Gibson, of
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,16,F"This has been an incredibly difficult
OL,17,Ffew years for Amelia's family and
OL,18,Ffriends and my thoughts are with them
OL,19,Ffollowing today's sentencing.
