OL,7,F"Welch's failure to carry out
OL,8,Fmandatory observations, lost any
OL,9,Fopportunity to prevent Amelia taking
OL,10,Fthese actions or possible
OL,11,Finterventions to save her life.
OL,13,F"The creation of false records in an
OL,14,Fattempt to cover her back was
OL,15,Fparticularly damning.
OL,17,F"I would like to thank Amelia's loved
OL,18,Fones for their dignified determination
OL,19,Fto pursue these criminal charges and
OL,20,Fhope that today provides them with
OL,21,Fsome closure."
